All Classes

  • All Classes Interface Summary Class Summary Enum Summary 
    Class Description
    Language
    Enumeration of all 235 languages contained in the Wikipedia Language Identification (WiLi) database.
    LanguageEntry
    Object that represents a singe k-mer/n-gram, along with its frequency and ranking.
    Menu
    Class for displaying a simple console based menu to the user.
    Parser<T>
    This class serves as the root class of all parser classes.
    Query
    An object that will be passed to QueryParser for parsing.
    QueryFile
    Object that creates a query file that can then be parsed by a QueryParser.
    QueryParser
    This class parses a query.
    QueryString
    Object that creates a query string that can then be parsed by a QueryParser.
    Runner
    Entry Point to the application.
    Script
    Utility class that can determine which Unicode block a given String belongs to.
    SubjectDatabase
    Class that stores a mapping of n-grams for each Language that is parsed by the SubjectParser.
    SubjectParser
    This class is responsible for parsing the subject dataset file.
